        },
        {
          "id": "a9c13431fa38_12",
          "href": null,
          "name": "ced9",
          "text": "Or said another way, we only get to the future that we all strive for together.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "a9c13431fa38_13",
          "href": null,
          "name": "87bc",
          "text": "Right now, the future is being shaped by those who hold us in fear and divide us against each other. They use our illusions of separation to get us fighting our allies when we should be planting seeds for a regenerative future. Nothing less will be worthy of our children’s inheritance.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "a9c13431fa38_14",
          "href": null,
          "name": "bc78",
          "text": "Let us together be wise managers of evolutionary change. We don’t have any more time to waste.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "a9c13431fa38_15",
          "href": null,
          "name": "8c84",
          "text": "Onward, fellow humans.",
